headline: Garret Talks About His Trip To Mar-a-Lago & Time With President Trump
author: Garret Lewis
sentences: Garret and his wife went to a Kari Lake fundraiser at Mar-a-Lago hosted by President Trump and were able to get a few minutes with President Trump.
He talks about things President Trump said, describes how gorgeous Mar-a-Lago is and being attacked for not wearing a mask.
